title: added cast to Date for zoo objects. Added tests
body: Good afternoon. When the patterns' zoo objects use POSIXct or POSIXlt instead of Date, the machine runs out of memory. I added a cast form POSIXct or POSIXlt to Date in the class "twdtwTimeSeries" line 81. This avoids the  issue #6. Besides, I added tests to make sure the cast is happening. Bests
